Multi-select filters
- Objective
Customers should be able to select multiple filters simultaneously in the gift finder. Multi-select must be supported within the category and store filters.
- Task Description
Within this task, we are building the ability to use multi-select within the category and store filters for the web.
- Reason
Based on user research and opinions, it has become clear that there is a need for broader searching using multi-select and the combination of store and category filters.
